---
title: Smart Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto Shrimp with Roasted Veggies and Cauliflower Rice
description: Craving pasta without wanting the carbs? This dinner packs all the flavours of a sun-dried tomato pesto pasta dinner, but with a garlicky cauliflower base!

